Package: hmsidwR
Title: Health Metrics and the Spread of Infectious Diseases
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Federica", "Gazzelloni", , "fede.gazzelloni@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4285-611X"))
Description: A collection of data and functions used in the Health Metrics and the Spread of Infectious Diseases book. The book provides the tools for calculating the DALYs (YLLs+YLDs), and other important health metrics. It also shows the R code for modeling infectious diseases with machine learning. Finally, allows the user to understand how to visualize the results and making maps. Gazzelloni (2024) <doi:10.5281/zenodo.10818338>.
